Package edu.ucla.wise.client.admin

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DropSurvey  
    PrefaceLoader
    PrefaceLoader is a class, which includes both welcome page and consent form (optional) (continue running the URL request from the admin - load.jsp)
    PrintSurveyServlet
    PrintSurveyServlet is a class used when user tries to print the survey page by page as in the survey XML form wise admin system.
    ReloadServlet
    ReloadServlet class is used to load a new survey and set up its Data tables.
    SurveyHealthLoaderServlet
    SurveyHealthLoaderServlet class is used to laod the method which checks the status of the survey system.
    SurveyLoaderServlet
    SurveyLoaderServlet class is used to load a new survey and set up its Data tables and also archives old tables.
    SurveyUpdateServlet
    SurveyUpdateServlet is a class which is used to update the local survey info Called by the Admin tool's drop_survey.jsp page *assuming* no error SurveyStatus param to indicate change requested.
    ViewFormServlet
    ViewFormServlet class is used to view the survey (without data filled in) page by page through wise admin system.
    ViewResultsServlet
    ViewResultsServlet class used to view the survey results (with the summary of data) by page (viewed by admin on behalf of Admin Application).
